step_data.thought: I'm now on the URL Rewrites page in the Magento Admin panel. This is the correct place to configure URL Rewrites for SEO optimization. Looking at the page, I can see a list of existing URL rewrites. To configure a new URL rewrite for SEO optimization, I need to click the 'Add URL Rewrite' button at the top of the page. This will allow me to create a new URL rewrite rule that can help with SEO by creating more user-friendly and search engine friendly URLs.
